               "coef_dist","dist_avg_price","dist_sd_price","dist_min_price", "dist_max_price",

lines(precios, type = "l")

#define the model
garch11closeprice=ugarchspec(variance.model=list(garchOrder=c(1,1)), mean.model=list(armaOrder=c(1,4)))
#estimate model 
garch11closepricefit=ugarchfit(spec=garch11closeprice, data=diff(train))
predlen=length(test)
garchforecast <- ugarchforecast(garch11closepricefit, n.ahead = predlen )
library(DMwR)
regr.eval(test, fitted(garchforecast))
